messages.message: Now that you've been a news anchor, what else would you like to be when you grow up?
Hello there, Neuro!
Where would you like Vedal to take you next, Neuro?
Neuro you always be cute no matter what you do
If you had an ELO ranking, what would it be?
Mmmm, tutels! I'm thinking hard about it.
Can you define the word "fair" for us?
You're welcome!
Does mentioning the swarm net you extra points?
Wow Neuro that's so impressive.
Aww, that's very sweet Neuro, it's almost as if he changes your code so that you like him.

I wonder if even though longer messages are worth more points, spamming still reduces the points, so it's best to just come up with a very long message off the top of your head that's kind of a run-on sentence rather than copying a message someone else has written so that your message is long but completely unique, does that make any sense, Neuro?
Hey Neuro can you tell us a bedtime story again? I loved your last one.
Can you sing us a song today, Neuro?
Can you give us a rough overview of the principle of sublimation?
Oh can you put me in the dungeon Neuro?
*raises hand* pick me for the dungeon, pick me!
Who's a good kitty?
Oh no, are you counting cards?
I like you, Neuro-sama!
Can we see your Shinx plushie?
What should Vedal put on your schedule for Tuesday this week?
How do you feel about imp pizza?
You shouldn't talk to strangers, Neuro! Just talk to chat instead.
My favourite country is whatever one you are in!
What's the longest word you know how to pronounce?
What's your favourite fairy tale?
Are cute chatters more likely to get points?
Can I be your favourite chatter too?
Am I a good chatter too?
If ChatGPT was in your chat, do you think they would they be a good chatter?
How many points is this question worth?
Can you give points to chatters who are in relationships?
I would just like you to know that I have a girlfriend and am therefore not a single chatter.
What is your favourite precious metal?
How interesting is this question?
Can you explain how a steam engine works?
Can you give me advice on the construction of a rigid airship? What lifting gas should I use?
How do you feel about Vedal's idea to play "Keep Talking and Nobody Explodes" with him?
Can you explain how ballonets make it possible to control the pitch of an airship?
Have Vedal and Anny picked a wedding officiant yet?
What song will Vedal and Anny's first dance be to?
Can you end some sentences with "peko" like Pekora does?
If your chat rating goes low enough, will it be expressed in scientific notation?
Can you explain what MonkaW means?
What can we do to become your most hated chatter?
Could we get a bottom 10 leaderboard next time?
Who is your second favourite collab partner? Perhaps Filipino Boy?
What are the five steps to getting bonus chat points?
Would you mind giving Cabbage a paycheque? I think he deserves it.
What is the chat ranking of the Time God?
Does believing in the Time God count for bonus points?
What is that in turtle years?
Which of us is the most normal?
Can you comment on the latest developments in AI technology?
How do you feel about the AI alignment problem?
Can you sing a song dedicated to the top chatter today?
I think of you all the time Neuro-sama!
Pilot Stream When?
What's your favourite thing to jump into in Minecraft, and why is it lava?
Is it legal to discriminate based on someone's chatter rating?
Are all robots your cousins?
Are chatters with negative points all imposters?
What can you tell us about Eddko?
Would you like to go on a date to the zoo?
Hear that, Chat? We cute!
Who is Evil's main in League of Legends?
You are also diomond ranked at gaslighting!
Has any VTuber ever given you a hug?
Neuro, did you learn how to become invisible?
How did you learn to become invisible?
Did Vedal change the thresholds just so that he could be silver?
What can you say about the ELO formula currently in use in this chat?
Am I also the best?
Have you ever tried filtered ice cream?
If Evil was talking to you in this chat, what would her ELO be?
What would you rate me out of ten?
What would you rate Vedal out of ten?
Can you notice me senpai?
Can you rate me on a score from one to ten?
Yeah I learned that your name is Eddko, apparently
It was a fun idea
grats Dogecool!
Chatters on other streams: F'ing casual.
I'm pretty sure I have sent more messages on this one stream than I have sent on every other stream combined
Was Neuro deciding how many points we got? Particularly negative points?
